name: rojak
description: [003] Rojak is a popular evening snack among Singaporeans, made up of deep fried batter-coated vegetables and meat, chopped up and served with peanut sauce. /// the circle of food by moth1 is a series of photographs of popular dishes from southeast Asia, digitally mirrored to form a geometric image, and then split into layers to create a parallax effect. 1000px, 15s mp4 looping video.
